  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `v2022.07.01` (Docker image on Kuberneted)\r\n\r\nDuring Sepolia merge, I used multiple combos:\r\n\r\n1. Geth - Teku\r\n2. Geth - Prysm\r\n3. **Erigon - Teku**\r\n\r\nEverything went well for combos 1. and 2., however for combo 3. (Erigon - Teku) our validators missed some attestations right after the merge.\r\n\r\nExample of missed attestation:\r\n<img width=\"468\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4943830/177580164-e28dd0fc-a910-45c2-92b7-35c3ecbc5ed6.png\">\r\n\r\nhttps://sepolia.beaconcha.in/validator/8bb045e7482b7abe670d72eb2f7afe4207b5a3d488364ff7bb4266f8784ea41893553a4bf7d01e78c99ed9008e2c13bb\r\n\r\nI'm not 100% sure it is Erigon related (might be Teku), but since my combo 1. did not had any issue, I assume it is Erigon related.\r\n\r\nPlease find the logs bellow for:\r\n- Erigon\r\n- Teku Beacon\r\n- Teku Validator\r\n\r\n**Erigon:**\r\nhttps://pastebin.com/04Fp9meu\r\n\r\n**Teku Beacon:**\r\nhttps://pastebin.com/rX6JAjZM\r\n\r\n**Teku Validator**\r\nhttps://pastebin.com/ha4bWbH7\r\n\r\n\r\n",
